What are cookies?
Cookies and tracking technologies are small text files that are stored on your device when you use a browser. 
Some cookies are essential to enable you to use our website, 
while other cookies collect information about your browsing habits. 
We use this data to offer you the best possible experience.


Why cookies?

Essential cookies ensure, 
for example, that you can securely log in and use our website. 
These cookies help us to protect your account and prevent fraud.
